                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "You were raised in the void of Wildspace—home to asteroid miners, moon farmers, and other hardy folk. Perhaps you grew up in a far-flung settlement such as the Rock of Bral, or you spent your early years on the crew of a spelljamming ship, performing helpful chores such as swabbing the deck, loading and offloading cargo, and scraping barnacles off the hull."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
