            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "em",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Whatever your history, life in Wildspace has toughened you so well that you are as brave as a miniature giant space hamster when it comes to facing the terrors and other challenges of the airless night."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
